social_posts.post_text: The reindeer came to visit, backyard sledding and snowstorms…all in less than a day ☃️❄️🦌 happy holidays!! #deer #colorado #holiday #family
All things pink and deer in the month of December 💖🦄
Vacay baddies!!! Me and my copilot keeping this long break from school going…we ain’t playing around 🫶🏽 I think we forgot what school even looks like at this point 😁
Fresh snow fall and a couple of lessons and he’s off 💥💥 so proud of my guy #myboyJulian for being way braver than I’ll ever be 🫶🏽
Always sim but diff 🐾. @andamasha
You’re literally stuck with me forever 😁 happy bday to the person that changed my life! @mashamandzuka you’re one in a million ❣️ @andamasha

When 2 to becomes 3…what an absolute icon @diane_keaton !! We have channeled your perfect style since day 1 and little do you know we even have a hat line dedicated for women like us who love a good men’s look ❤️ we bow to you 🙌🏽 @andamasha ❤️#AndaMashaHats

Teenage bucket list come true 🤙🏽 #keanureeves ❤️ and working with Keanu + DogStar was 🔥 Favorite line #billandtedsexcellentadventure ‘Be excellent to eachother, and party on dude!’ 🤟🏾#wyldstallyns #matrix #dogstar #bestoftheday #picoftheday x @andamasha #AndaMashaHats
Favorite all times…denim jacket ↠ ↠ ↠ L❤️VE #keanureeves #billandtedsexcellentadventure ✌🏽✌🏽
Our muse in life @diane_keaton ♕ Always love working with @jcrew ♡ Hats and suits all day ♡ @andamasha

To know you is to absolutely adore and love you…❤️ happy birthday to this super human who brings all sorts of ppl together  @brianbowensmith 💋💋 + thanks for being our new bud #KeanuReeves #excellent 🤟🏾#bestoftheday #picoftheday
Forever this connection 🫶🏽 #myboyJulian #mothersday #love #picoftheday 🌀 And forever reminding myself that I can do this 🤟🏾 strength is from within ❤️
Your mood is my mood #myboyJulian ✌🏽but I do recommend everyone having this event at their party 🌼🌾🌷thanks for the new hair accessory @christianmarc 🫶🏽

I cannot possibly love you more. At 10 years old you are creative, kind and thoughtful more than any years ever taught me to be. Here’s to a DECADE- how the good times fly- and MANY MORE!! 🤟🏾❤️ forever #MyBoyJulian ❤️ #family #momlife Happy July 4!!
Ten days of jungle living with little Wi-Fi, loads of nighttime storms and lots of friendship and love 🌈🐒 #PuraVida #CostaRica #myboyJulian #bestoftheday #picoftheday
Forever STILL laughing w this one @mashamandzuka 🐒
Sweet reels compilation of our shoot with Keanu and @dogstarband 🫶🏽 shot by @brianbowensmith ❤️ @andamasha #picoftheday #keanureeves
This just feels like one of those moments I need to hold on to… 🤍 go get ‘em Julian 🫶🏽

Every single moment counts. Thank you for these incredible memories during a time in the world where I just want to keep these kids even closer 🥺❣️ We laughed, we shared, we froze and we conquered…and this is what it’s all about 🌵
Leave me alone…it’s December ! 🥶
I love a fun birthday 🔥 and I love you all for celebrating with me 🫶🏽 HAPPY HOLIDAYS everyone…I’m a Xmas baby!
Our tree is filled with menorahs, dreidels, Xmas ornaments and Smurfs! Some of us grow up in mixed households so whatever and whoever you are… Happy Holidays from our fam to yours ❣️🎄🕎 🪅🎎🧸 just L❤️VE
Aloha 🤙🏾🌈 happy happy 2024
Always together…always mad at me 🤣…always laughing ❣️ happy new year @andamasha
